{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:08.788487+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the setup and development commands for this repository (**vue3-vite-starter-template**):\n\n---\n\n### Requirements\n\n- **Node.js**: v24 (per `.nvmrc`)\n- **Package manager**: pnpm 10.20.0 (enforced — `preinstall` script blocks npm/yarn via `only-allow pnpm`)\n\n---\n\n### Setup\n\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Dev Server (hot-reload)\n\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Build (production)\n\n```bash\npnpm run build\n```\n\n### Preview (production build locally)\n\n```bash\npnpm run preview\n```\nOr combined:\n```bash\npnpm run build-preview\n```\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit\n```\nWith coverage:\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit-coverage\n```\n\n### Lint\n\n```bash\npnpm run lint        # Check only\npnpm run lint-fix    # Auto-fix\n```\n\n### Other Notes\n\n- **Prettier** is configured (`prettier.config.js`) for code formatting.\n- **Husky** + **lint-staged** + **commitlint** are set up for pre-commit hooks (commit message linting with conventional commits).\n- **Vitest** is the test runner; **ESLint** is the linter; **Vite** is the build tool.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 323, "prompt_tokens": 9328, "total_tokens": 9651, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 22, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8832, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0001846096, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.41696e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 9.044e-05}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871223-QBbkZg0f0p1NOjEMcqdU", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea432-58fd-7cc3-9dc5-896159f78e34-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9328, "output_tokens": 323, "total_tokens": 9651, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8832}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 22}}}}]}}}
